# Click on the Label gadget. 
# Move the pointer in and out of the client window,
# once with MB1 pressed, and  once with it released. 

CompareVisual Shell1
LocatePointer LabelGadget1
ClickMB Btn1

LocatePointer Frame1 Off
LocatePointer LabelGadget1
LocatePointer Frame1 Off

PressMB Btn1
LocatePointer LabelGadget1
LocatePointer Frame1 Off
ReleaseMB Btn1

WindowIconify Shell1
WindowDeiconify Shell1
Continue

# The gnu pixmap should appear on the label gadget.
# Click on the Label gadget. 
# Move the pointer in and out of the client window,
# once with MB1 pressed, and once with it released. 

CompareVisual Frame1

LocatePointer LabelGadget1
ClickMB Btn1

LocatePointer Frame1 Off
LocatePointer LabelGadget1
LocatePointer Frame1 Off

PressMB Btn1
LocatePointer LabelGadget1
LocatePointer Frame1 Off
ReleaseMB Btn1

Continue

Exit


